    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_52_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_02_01-kan002.m4a",
      "text": "さっむ、うっざ！　おい{user}！\nいつまでkanaを待たせる訳！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s freezing! So annoying! Hey‚ {user}!\nHow long are you gonna keep kana waiting!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 35.0666670482,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hokkatown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hokkatown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 37.7436369143
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_52_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_02_01-kan003.m4a",
      "text": "早くタクシー拾って来いよ！\n……ったく、これで旅館ボロかったら許さないから！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hurry up and grab us a taxi already!\n…Seriously‚ if the inn turns out to be crappy‚ I won’t forgive you!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 40.582566341,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hokkatown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hokkatown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 44.9400324706
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_52_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_02_01-smr002.m4a",
      "text": "うう……さとみさんがもう暖かいから薄着で\n大丈夫かもって言ってたけど……意外と寒いです！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ugh… Satomi said it was already warm enough\nthat light clothes would be fine‚ but… it’s colder than I expected!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 49.6158999287,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_52_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_02_01-rei002.m4a",
      "text": "そうね……私も沙季の言う通り上着でも\n持って来れば良かったわ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah… I should’ve listened to Saki and brought\nan extra jacket too…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 59.5666673025,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hokkatown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hokkatown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 62.1542242572
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_52_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_02_01-rei003.m4a",
      "text": "それにしても、一番北海道を楽しみにしてたさくらが\nやけに静かだけど……って、さくら！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "By the way‚ Sakura was the one most excited for Hokkaido‚\nbut she’s awfully quiet… wait‚ Sakura!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 67.0333314261,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hokkatown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hokkatown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 71.8967416013
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_52_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_02_01-skr002.m4a",
      "text": "ブブブブブブ……！　ザザザザザンギ……！\nジジジジジンギスカン……！　ララララーメン……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "B-b-b-b-b…! Za-za-za-zangi…!\nJ-j-j-jingisukan…! R-r-r-ramen…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 76.2090948586,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hokkatown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hokkatown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 80.9596666222
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_52_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_02_01-yu002.m4a",
      "text": "あかん！　寒過ぎて痙攣してはる！\nはよ温めてあげな！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "This is bad! She’s shivering from the cold!\nHurry and warm her up!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 83.6333314261,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hokkatown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hokkatown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 85.6848329431
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_52_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_02_01-smr003_a.m4a",
      "text": "『おしくらまんじゅう』であっためるしかないです！\nさくらちゃん、しっかりして下さ～い！　ぎゅー！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We’ll just have to warm her up with a group hug!\nSakura‚ hang in there~! squeeze~!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 88.3009278462,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gasa-02.m4a",
