      "bgName": "hokkatown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 88.3009278462
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hokkatown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hokkatown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 90.9190692902
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hokkatown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hokkatown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 93.0177354382
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_52_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_02_01-skr003.m4a",
      "text": "……は、はふ～！　すみれちゃん、あったか～い……\nじゅわ～ってとろけたよ、ありがとう～！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…H-haaah~! Sumire-chan is so warm~…\nI totally melted~ thank you~!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 101.7342611795,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hokkatown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hokkatown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 106.3023614771
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_52_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_02_01-smr004.m4a",
      "text": "えへへ、どういたしまして！\nそれで、さっきはなんて言ってたんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ehehe‚ you’re welcome!\nSo‚ what were you saying earlier?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 109.2342611795,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hokkatown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hokkatown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 112.5150824752
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_52_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_02_01-skr004.m4a",
      "text": "ザンギッ！　ジンギスカンッ！　ラーメン！　だよ\nあぁ、今すぐ口一杯にほおばりたいなぁ……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Zangi! Jingisukan! Ramen!\nAhh‚ I want to stuff my mouth full right now…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 116.6675945128,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hokkatown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hokkatown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 121.9587753183
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_52_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_02_01-skr005.m4a",
      "text": "この旅行のために、昨日も遙子ちゃんのトンカツを\n我慢したんだ～。本当に辛い一週間だったよ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "For this trip‚ I even resisted Haruko’s tonkatsu\neven yesterday~ it was such a painful week…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 125.5342581277,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hokkatown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hokkatown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 131.5158954508
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_52_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_02_01-rei004.m4a",
      "text": "だから最近修行僧みたいな生活してたのね、さくら……\nでも、食べ過ぎには気を付けるのよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So that’s why you’ve been living like an ascetic monk lately…\nStill‚ be careful not to overeat‚ okay?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 136.2666581473,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hokkatown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hokkatown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 139.5577872481
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_52_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_02_01-skr006.m4a",
      "text": "北海道に降り立った私の辞書に『食べ過ぎ』なんて\n言葉はないよ、怜ちゃん！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The word “overeat” doesn’t exist in my dictionary\nonce I’ve landed in Hokkaido‚ Rei-chan!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 143.5094832584,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hokkatown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hokkatown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 145.8710615363
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_52_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_02_01-kan004.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ……スリクス三人の旅番組が嫌で\nこっちに来たけど、もう帰りたくなってきたわ",
      "translations": {
